{"tid":565210,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「拉闊style」抄原創仲聲大夾惡","createTime":"2018-02-18T17:56:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T11:04:35.000Z","uid":171432,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"73053779b36990c9f6c26245cc85b6a40b945f61","tid":565210,"uid":171432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T17:56:03.000Z","msg":"代朋友出文<br />\n話說尋日facebook個page出左篇野講旺角夜市<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/014601_64ff35d1c3468ab7d73960b999da6845.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F014601_64ff35d1c3468ab7d73960b999da6845.png&h=ac9c5c6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朋友個page一路都唔係用黎賺錢，純粹講下自己睇法，但估唔到篇文一夜爆紅，結果引左另一個page抄文<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/014830_d49c901194332d84bfae96f0ff3c8b60.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F014830_d49c901194332d84bfae96f0ff3c8b60.png&h=399fe27e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成篇文雖然用字改左，但根本個角度、思路，措詞都係非常相近，於是朋友係自己個page講返，被人抄文一事，仲有唔少網民係「拉闊style」個post留言話佢抄文。但結果⋯⋯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/015104_bc0743016a4665efc38d00f2b5b1c078.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F015104_bc0743016a4665efc38d00f2b5b1c078.png&h=ae6e29fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n朋友話其實原本佢悄悄delete 篇文都唔想搞大件事，但估唔到佢抄完文仲反串返留言嘅人。其實朋友個page啲文都係自己寫下感受，估唔到咁都有用黎扼like，真係好無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知各位ching知唔知呢個page是咩背景咩來頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14d32662e106547258897709c402d44c6d1e90a7","tid":565210,"uid":21483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T17:59:54.000Z","msg":"你的朋友就是⋯"},{"pid":"e4876dd77a2f4b7ab5fcd30bdb03369c0a524351","tid":565210,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:01:34.000Z","msg":"好似係咩lifetv其下分頁<br />\n好似果籽係蘋果啲細page咁"},{"pid":"dc63989b6362113d7ce5c78197ea750458191a2b","tid":565210,"uid":171432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14d32662e106547258897709c402d44c6d1e90a7","tid":565210,"uid":21483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T17:59:54.000Z","msg":"你的朋友就是⋯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:02:19.000Z","msg":"我都想係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4187067f3f86be66128ac4a1fb06fdde6d2e2c6e","tid":565210,"uid":171432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4876dd77a2f4b7ab5fcd30bdb03369c0a524351","tid":565210,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:01:34.000Z","msg":"好似係咩lifetv其下分頁<br />\n好似果籽係蘋果啲細page咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:04:17.000Z","msg":"Ching有冇多啲詳情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我見佢請到好多名星拍片，以為佢係唱片公司搞"},{"pid":"3efb0ef2849961e2c2a5ca313679693f894032bf","tid":565210,"uid":47055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:05:33.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"9c5c86ff9071dd729a94b5db36d3cdb12c46e6d8","tid":565210,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:05:57.000Z","msg":"Facebook search lifetv"},{"pid":"e4000991ec64391d76c34e6dce30eb038475385a","tid":565210,"uid":121240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:07:59.000Z","msg":"仲要咁臭串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec219565ee18b51398f94ea8207adfa6f9d0b79c","tid":565210,"uid":46336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:14:45.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"1bdaa5e7f05439df836ab3a6c98cab7148ddea64","tid":565210,"uid":171432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4000991ec64391d76c34e6dce30eb038475385a","tid":565210,"uid":121240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:07:59.000Z","msg":"仲要咁臭串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:20:05.000Z","msg":"呢個page仲要成7萬like<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9108fa5c4b3e30df6e08a080c1d03b70bdbfc1f","tid":565210,"uid":117005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:33:20.000Z","msg":"留名了解更多"},{"pid":"4a4110d7e6d9c51f97b56fcf9734687e77adbbee","tid":565210,"uid":63670,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:35:33.000Z","msg":"我唔理<br />\n抄人嘢仲要咁撚串就係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支持樓主<br />\npish"},{"pid":"9bda4194325d2616cfbd65faa2e59e84b101bbca","tid":565210,"uid":127469,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:53:10.000Z","msg":"講真個角度、思路，措詞都係陳腔濫掉，咁梗係差唔多喇<br />\n<br />\n好似呢篇2017年講夜市<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1047328\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1047328&d=yy7YXDl9ly5dWYWlFrbr4Bv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=19712cd6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1047328&h=2bb5cd4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1047328</a> <br />\n<br />\n隨意highlight幾句類似：<br />\n<br />\n香港人很有公民素養的，香港人很有公民素養的，香港人很有公民素養的。再三告訴自己。當了一晚清潔義工後，這句話完全被打臉。<br />\n<br />\n垃圾推車也顯然多了幾架，走多幾步就可順手一丟。遺憾的是，部份垃圾不在裏面，反而堆積在店鋪門口、階梯、走廊&hellip; 噢還有在垃圾袋旁邊，而垃圾袋還是扁塌塌的，尚餘空間收集。<br />\n<br />\n我和朋友約凌晨一點開始從砵蘭街（H＆M作為起點）「掃街」，無功而返。不到十五分鐘，清理好的角落轉眼又堆滿垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n深入虎穴龍潭，慘不忍睹，到處垃坡小山，有相憑證，不是唬爛。大量發泡膠兜、膠叉、竹籤、膠袋、膠樽、食物殘骸&hellip;隨處可見，亂丟者責無旁貸。<br />\n<br />\n新年本應開心如意，但幾晚夜市見真章，盡顯港人浪費心態與處置垃圾的惰性。"},{"pid":"aa4e1458cdd98048d7a69d416c7f4e39964a9c1d","tid":565210,"uid":57447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a4110d7e6d9c51f97b56fcf9734687e77adbbee","tid":565210,"uid":63670,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:35:33.000Z","msg":"我唔理<br />\n抄人嘢仲要咁撚串就係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支持樓主<br />\npish"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T22:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60927bec35f3329c14c0977b31a2517cf653804b","tid":565210,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa4e1458cdd98048d7a69d416c7f4e39964a9c1d","tid":565210,"uid":57447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a4110d7e6d9c51f97b56fcf9734687e77adbbee","tid":565210,"uid":63670,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:35:33.000Z","msg":"我唔理<br />\n抄人嘢仲要咁撚串就係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支持樓主<br />\npish"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T22:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T22:23:46.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"82a04a43f5d2b44b9e71e59db9aad0aa5872be4a","tid":565210,"uid":37747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T22:36:59.000Z","msg":"咪好似跑步游水咁，人做乜你做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082d3fd0f35d0d7c285446307f5dde102fe53088","tid":565210,"uid":28759,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T23:29:00.000Z","msg":"坦白講<br />\n你話係抄又得<br />\n拉闊話佢冇抄都得<br />\n<br />\n初一夜市污糟<br />\n我諗係路人皆見<br />\n題材內容都唔係好獨到<br />\n有乜好抄定唔抄<br />\n<br />\n相又唔同<br />\n用詞遣字又唔一樣<br />\n咁你講污糟來來去去都係咁㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n坦白講<br />\n你毎 point 冇返咁上下獨到<br />\n憑咩覺得你係自己諗<br />\n人地就係抄<br />\n<br />\n有邊個初一經過朗豪<br />\n係覺得好乾淨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港人唔配有XX<br />\n呢個句式拾俯皆是啦<br />\n嬲嚟都多餘"},{"pid":"a84351ffe6f7cadc56329a7b9ab04f302213cab7","tid":565210,"uid":168222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T23:36:56.000Z","msg":"乜都炒呢啲人真係冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e065b5419f8ea0fbf28e7efdedc7e5d7f6b87f10","tid":565210,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T00:24:29.000Z","msg":"正仆街"},{"pid":"becebe2c01d8212df4ad9fe2084edbb1ba624af2","tid":565210,"uid":17496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T00:32:24.000Z","msg":"老實講就咁睇又唔覺抄，但佢咁留言我就覺得佢擺明抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f17994b8d2e822aa467d59e455f5eb27e9ee1470","tid":565210,"uid":171432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"082d3fd0f35d0d7c285446307f5dde102fe53088","tid":565210,"uid":28759,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T23:29:00.000Z","msg":"坦白講<br />\n你話係抄又得<br />\n拉闊話佢冇抄都得<br />\n<br />\n初一夜市污糟<br />\n我諗係路人皆見<br />\n題材內容都唔係好獨到<br />\n有乜好抄定唔抄<br />\n<br />\n相又唔同<br />\n用詞遣字又唔一樣<br />\n咁你講污糟來來去去都係咁㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n坦白講<br />\n你毎 point 冇返咁上下獨到<br />\n憑咩覺得你係自己諗<br />\n人地就係抄<br />\n<br />\n有邊個初一經過朗豪<br />\n係覺得好乾淨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港人唔配有XX<br />\n呢個句式拾俯皆是啦<br />\n嬲嚟都多餘"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T03:39:51.000Z","msg":"當然唔一定係隻隻字一樣先叫抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢成篇文嘅脈絡，一開始就用返香港人不配乜乜乜<br />\n然後第二句已經用政府隻眼開隻眼閉。<br />\n<br />\n再去第二段同樣用台灣人做比喻，指台灣人帶走垃圾<br />\n至最後呼籲市民，成篇野脈絡一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a1b6a6d8e74ae7f3c9e23691c3fca1f0b09c0c","tid":565210,"uid":171432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T14:17:22.000Z","msg":"最新進展，呢個page真係好串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/19/221623_c43e810bddada59101daaf6634795003.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F19%2F221623_c43e810bddada59101daaf6634795003.png&h=b05ea727&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e8c0d48b6a51401560a90b9ebef3592f54fba8a6","tid":565210,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T06:47:50.000Z","msg":"夜市講台灣好出奇咩？<br />\n呼籲人整返乾淨好出奇咩？<br />\n坦白講你篇所謂「原文」<br />\n係人都寫得出啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小氣完未<br />\n仲勞師動眾話人抄你<br />\n人唔笑狗都吠啦下話"},{"pid":"d34c9df267b85f59fc3dc6913fa9b5b18afd6572","tid":565210,"uid":34472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4187067f3f86be66128ac4a1fb06fdde6d2e2c6e","tid":565210,"uid":171432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4876dd77a2f4b7ab5fcd30bdb03369c0a524351","tid":565210,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:01:34.000Z","msg":"好似係咩lifetv其下分頁<br />\n好似果籽係蘋果啲細page咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T18:04:17.000Z","msg":"Ching有冇多啲詳情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/